metadata.name: Estrella
metadata.description:
Daydreamer: Estrella

Daydreamers represents the fine line between reality and imagination, how we can create something surreal from something as simple and natural as a flower, and how a flower can become a dream of desire and melancholy as one wanders lulled by its constant motion.

Estrella dreams quietly in a dark green sky full of little white star-shaped flowers.

Through my art, I like to show our vulnerability, our personality, and feelings, everything that makes us human and connects us with ourselves and with nature.

This collection is a mix of my photography interlaced with Ai and digitally retouched.

--
